text: <!channel> I've been working a little on the landing page for the chrome extension I built and would love your feedback if/when you have a few minute. It's just a draft and I haven't "designed" anything in a while so don't hesitate to bring anything up.

attachments.title: Jeff Bridges Stars in the First Super Bowl Ad That Actually Wants to Put You to Sleep
attachments.text: Kia may have James Bond in its Super Bowl ad, but Squarespace has the Dude. Yes, Jeff Bridges, the Oscar winner and star of cult classic The Big Lebowski, is featured in Squarespace's 30-second ad, from Wieden + Kennedy in New York.
